Package: locu
Type: Package
Title: Lorenz curves with ggplot2 and some common inequality measures.
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jakob", "Bossek", email = "j.bossek@gmail.com", role =
    c("aut", "cre")))
Encoding: UTF-8
Description: Draw Lorenz curves with the popular ggplot2 package and
    compute different inequality measures such as the Gini coefficient.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jbossek/locu
BugReports: https://github.com/jbossek/locu/issues
Depends:
    ggplot2,
    BBmisc (>= 1.6)
Imports:
    checkmate (>= 1.1)
Suggests:
    testthat
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
